b.	Create an inventory team to conduct a complete physical count / inventory of all properties in accordance with existing regulations and in order to establish the actual existence;
c.	Submit a complete Report on the Physical Count of Property, Plant and Equipment & Inventory and Inspection Report of Unserviceable Property (IIRUP) to the Accounting Office for reconciliation with the latter's ledger cards;
